com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.core.refset.automap

Interface ITableParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CsvVariableFieldCountParser, XlsParser

    public interface ITableParser
    Interface for parsing table-like files (eg. xls). Skipping empty lines and headers must be supported and can be controlled by the parser.
